ed to the character.\r\n\r\nThe data you are pointing to allows to generate images, but not videos unfortunately. You can generate videos though with the data from our latest watch and help paper: http://virtual-home.org/release/watch_and_help/watch_data.zip. You will see a sequence of programs that you can render and obtain semantic segmentation. From there you can train a model for object detection.\r\n\r\nHope this helps","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/xavierpuigf/virtualhome/issues/comments/770048680/reactions","total_count":2,"+1":2,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"xavierpuigf","id":4203263,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQyMDMyNjM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4203263?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/xavierpuigf","html_url":"https://github.com/xavierpuigf","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/xavierpuigf/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/xavierpuigf/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/xavierpuigf/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/xavierpuigf/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/xavierpuigf/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/xavierpuigf/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/xavierpuigf/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/xavierpuigf/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/xavierpuigf/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false}},{"id":4268036209,"node_id":"MDE0Ok1lbnRpb25lZEV2ZW50NDI2ODAzNjIwOQ==","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/xavierpuigf/virtualhome/issues/events/4268036209","actor":{"login":"yunsujeon","id":38097792,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM4MDk3Nzky","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38097792?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/yunsujeon"